{"tid":931628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【職場熱話】為求加薪　甘與上司上床　調查：事後男比女易獲晉升","createTime":"2018-12-07T07:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T13:45:36.000Z","uid":117200,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"708572fe0b00861f948b2cf13b1bb9c4bcc3b261","tid":931628,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"為升職加薪，打工仔甘願以身體換取機會？這像是電視劇的情節，但國外一項調查發現，分別有接近3成的女性及男生員工承認曾這樣做，其中約四分之一的人最終與上級進行了性行為，並獲加薪、晉升待遇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（9.7%） 「希望增加假期或病假」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2155005/org/07da88824e0f5eb90f9c4f769c504af5.jpg/YS5UzTNV0WuRPbkzclZyhbHsVgSuq-AehoP5qYaD-ak\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2155005%2Forg%2F07da88824e0f5eb90f9c4f769c504af5.jpg%2FYS5UzTNV0WuRPbkzclZyhbHsVgSuq-AehoP5qYaD-ak&h=aec05ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（8.3%） 有些人的原因並非單為自己獲利，有人表示「希望幫助同事獲得加薪」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2154989/org/6181025c0a86311976c19da6bb3a2eed.jpg/zcOrEuE8oZAYgoutNQjmyfxJ2KNG08lH6cm0bunJtG4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2154989%2Forg%2F6181025c0a86311976c19da6bb3a2eed.jpg%2FzcOrEuE8oZAYgoutNQjmyfxJ2KNG08lH6cm0bunJtG4&h=de5a82dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（7.3％）「試圖讓朋友獲得聘用」<br />\n<img src=\"https://ak4.picdn.net/shutterstock/videos/14479624/thumb/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fak4.picdn.net%2Fshutterstock%2Fvideos%2F14479624%2Fthumb%2F1.jpg&h=f92e30c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一現象是受訪者得悉其他同事與老闆發生性關係後，有（6.6%）的人表示他們想與該位同事發生性關係。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.brockoa.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/B138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.brockoa.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FB138.jpg&h=36cbf368&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6b699d0b12c356224b1b7f1c5593be3e24e9aa0","tid":931628,"uid":8264